---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/base.css";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main class="privacy-container">
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="effective-date">Last Updated: November 7, 2025</p>

      <p class="intro">
        Welcome to the Corespark Community Center. This privacy policy explains
        how we handle information. Our guiding principle is to protect your
        privacy and collect as little information as possible.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Privacy is Our Priority</h2>
      <p>
        We built this community center to provide help, not to harvest your
        personal data. We respect the privacy of every visitor, especially those
        seeking resources.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong
          >We do not require you to log in, create an account, or provide any
          personal information</strong
        > to use this site.
      </p>

      <h2>What Information We Collect (and Why)</h2>
      <p>
        We collect only one type of information: anonymous website analytics.
      </p>

      <h3 class="gradient-text">Simple Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        We use an analytics tool called
        <a
          href="https://www.simpleanalytics.com/?referral=ruwef"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          style="color: var(--accent-color); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;"
        >
          Simple Analytics
        </a> to help us understand how our site is being used. We intentionally chose this tool because of the privacy-respecting practices that they follow and that the information collected <span
          style="color: var(--accent-color); font-weight: 600"
          >cannot be used to identify you</span
        > ensuring that your privacy on the community center is respected.
      </p>
      <p>The data we look at includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The pages you visit (e.g., "Food Pantries")</li>
        <li>The type of device you are using (e.g., mobile or desktop)</li>
        <li>
          Your general geographic region (e.g., North Carolina, but not your
          city or street)
        </li>
        <li>The website that referred you (e.g., a Google search)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We use this data <strong>only</strong> to improve the website for everyone.
        By seeing which resources are most popular, we know where to focus our efforts.
        By checking device types, we can make sure the site is easy to use on a phone.
      </p>

      <p>
        For more information about Simple Analytics and their privacy practices,
        please visit <a
          href="https://docs.simpleanalytics.com/what-we-collect"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >https://docs.simpleanalytics.com/what-we-collect</a
        >
      </p>

      <h2>What We <span class="gradient-text">Do Not</span> Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>We DO NOT</strong> use invasive tracking tools.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>We DO NOT</strong> track you across other websites or apps.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>We DO NOT</strong> sell or share your data with any third parties.
          Period.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We do not use any cookies to track out activity. Our analytics provider
        does not use cookies either.
      </p>

      <h2>Links to Other Websites</h2>
      <p>
        Our site, especially the food pantry map, contains links to other
        websites (like a pantry's homepage). If you click on a third-party link,
        you will be directed to that site.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please be aware that we have no control over, and assume no
        responsibility for, the content or privacy practices of these external
        sites.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted
        on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices,
        please email us at:
        <a href="mailto:community@corespark.io">community@corespark.io</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .privacy-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto 4rem;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .content h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .effective-date {
      color: var(--text-color, #444);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .intro {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .content ul {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }
    .content li {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .content a {
      color: var(--accent-color, blue);
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
